  out into a separate PR.
* There are some outstanding review comments that I need to look into further.
* ramoops isn't working yet, it appears that APBoot clears the RAM on boot.
  Might be something we can patch out as well.

[^1]: https://github.com/lukasstockner/ap325-apboot-openwrt

